## The Dockerfile

I used Visual Studio Code to add a Dockerfile to the project. I opened the Command Palette (⇧⌘P) and used the "Docker: Add Docker Files to Workspace..." command:

FROM node:12.18-alpine

ENV NODE_ENV=production

WORKDIR /usr/src/app

COPY ["package.json", "package-lock.json*", "npm-shrinkwrap.json*", "./"]

RUN npm install --production --silent && mv node_modules ../

COPY . .

EXPOSE 5000

CMD ["npm", "start"]

